description:
Applicability
This schedule applies to: 1) commercial and industrial customers for general power use with a demand of 500 to 2,999 kW, and 2) services where other Rate Schedules (other than Rate Schedules NM and SG) do not apply. This schedule is applicable on an annual basis only.
Power Factor Charge, per kVAr $ 1.10
name: Schedule HT Large Industrial Service - Demand Metered 500 to 2,999 kW, Time-Of-Use
